Author: softcoffee
Text: Calorie counting is a slippery slope waiting for me to break my neck on it. I started tracking in MFP yesterday (downloaded it for the first time), but I feel calmer not getting caught up in the number. I try to prioritize macros because I know protein makes it easier to restrict without thinking too much about it daily.   I can definitely relate. It feels like a load of my mind to not have so many numbers in my head all day.
